dct_description_sm: "Nộp lưu chiẻ̂u tháng ơ năm 2001." Ancillary map: Phân bố các dân tộc theo ngữ hệ. [Distribution of ethnic groups according to linguistic families] Includes population growth graphs (1921-1999), population by age and sex 1989 and 1999,  education  and occupation chart by region .
